    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>1- You should group by ID and count each items:</p>\n<pre><code>SELECT *, COUNT(*) AS count FROM Userdetails GROUP BY ID\n</code></pre>\n<p>2- Then give it a name and use its result for sorting:</p>\n<pre><code>SELECT * FROM ( SELECT *, COUNT(*) AS count FROM Userdetails GROUP BY ID ) innerQuery \nORDER BY innerQuery.count DESC\n</code></pre>\n<p>and in your code sample:</p>\n<pre><code>Cursor cursor = DB.rawQuery(&quot;SELECT * FROM ( SELECT *, COUNT(*) AS count FROM Userdetails GROUP BY ID ) innerQuery ORDER BY innerQuery.count DESC&quot;, null);\n</code></pre>\n"
