  "body" : "<p>I'm having a problem querying a SQLite database in Android. The way I do it now is only <code>ORDER BY</code>, but it doesn't work, only the sorting function.</p>\n<pre><code>Cursor cursor = DB.rawQuery(&quot;SELECT * FROM Userdetails ORDER BY ID DESC&quot;, null);\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/bD6IK.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">enter image description here</a></p>\n<p>How to query all the most similar values ​​in the <code>ID</code> column? In this case <code>1ABC</code> occurs at most so it should appear twenty-two times.</p>\n"
